   </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">This deck strangles your opponents magi. With the power of Xyx, Thunder Hyren, and Ground Breaker you can attack the magi directly. You can also make use of such cards as Arderial&#39;s Crown, and Ora&#39;s power to make your creatures powerful. You are also protected from a variety of regions. The Yarothis provides good defense against core. The Flutter Yup provides good defense for your magi against Kybar&#39;s Teeth (this is mainly because practically every Kybar&#39;s Teeth creature has more than three energy), and Brannix is pretty good against Arderial Creatures. The deck is simple, and of course there is room for improvement. I&#39;m fairly new to the game, and I was tempted to put this deck in the beginner section, but it uses a variety of rares. Constuctive criticism is welcome just don&#39;t be too harsh with the rating :) Thanks a lot, and hopefully I&#39;ll be back with something better next time.  </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
